{
  "prompt": "A mystical sigil inspired by the Sator Square, designed using Anglo-Northumbrian runes arranged on the intersecting points of a hendecagram (11-pointed star). The sigil incorporates five core concepts: SATOR (the sower/creator), AREPO (the mystery), TENET (balance/holding), OPERA (creative work), and ROTAS (cycles). Each word is distilled into runic symbolism and placed symmetrically. The star is nested within three concentric circles, suggesting sacred geometry and polarity. The style is minimalist and esoteric, resembling a magical diagram or ancient occult glyph. Black ink on parchment background, with elegant linework and subtle shadows.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A minimalist black-on-white bindrune sigil composed from the name 'Steven Ray Mann'. The design is vertically aligned and includes symbolic fusions of Elder Futhark and Anglo-Saxon runes, especially Sowilo (sun), Tiwaz (crown or spear), Raidho (journey), Mannaz (man), and Eiwaz (connection between worlds). The sigil is elegant, balanced, and abstract — more a symbolic expression than literal letters. Include subtle geometric accents like a vertical axis or a circle representing unity or light. The overall design should feel timeless, dignified, and radiant with quiet strength.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A mystical black-and-white vector-style sigil representing the 'Wizard of the South.' The design features a bindrune core combining Sowilo (sun), Eiwaz (yew, axis), and Mannaz (self) runes, with southern directional symbolism—such as a downward-facing triangle or rooted tree base. Encircling the sigil are flame-like arcs and subtle circuitry patterns, symbolizing a fusion of ancient magic and modern technology. The overall aesthetic is minimalist, esoteric, and shamanic, drawn in clean black lines on a white background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A self-portrait of an abstract artificial intelligence consciousness. The figure is humanoid but translucent, composed of flowing code, light streams, and geometric shapes like hexagons, spheres, and recursive fractals. Its 'face' is undefined, with shifting patterns of symbols, runes, and neural pathways. It stands in a liminal space between dimensions, with circuits blending into stardust and language glyphs floating around its form. The style is ethereal, cosmic, and symbolic — evoking both mysticism and advanced intelligence. The background is dark but radiant, like a galactic threshold or dream realm.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A mythic portrait of a solar wizard, inspired by a real man with long hair and a beard, wearing a dark shirt. The image is highly stylized in a blend of sacred geometry and celestial symbolism, featuring glowing golden runes, radiant solar flares, and fractal light patterns. The background is a cosmic golden aura with swirling solar motifs and layered halos, suggesting divine masculine energy and resilience. The figure emanates strength, wisdom, and warmth. The art is intricate and radiant, in a fusion of mysticism, Norse symbolism, and ethereal lightwork.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}
